Users use cases:

All Users have the same Bio attributes (
 first_name:string
 last_name:string
 username:string
 date_of_birth:date
 place_of_birth:string
 gender:string
 phone1:string
 phone2:string
 email:string
 password:string
 address_line:string
 city:string
 country:string
 is_active:boolean
 is_deleted:boolean
 photo_data:binary
 
 )
 
 and a Profile (linked profiles_table) attributes

A Student < Users and has these attributes (
 student_id:integer
 group:string
 enrollment_date:date
 guardian_id:integer FK
)
and a Student association goes as follow: 
 belongs_to :user
 belongs_to :group
 
 has_many :guardians
 has_many :attendances
 has_many :courses
 has_many :exam_grades
 has_many :finance_fees
 
An Employee < Users and has these attributes (
 employee_id:integer
 employee_category:string
 experience_years:integer
 employee_level:string
 employee_qualification:string
 start_date:date
)

A Guardian < Users and has these attributes (
 guardian_id:integer
 relation:string
 occupation:string
)



